* The primary objective of Armeniaâs energy sector development strategy is to formulate strategic goals for the development of the energy system in Armenia and identify the avenues to achieve those goals, based on the principles adopted by the international community for sustainable development, particularly in the energy sector, and guided by the directions of economic development in the Republic of Armenia and past energy sector experience..
